195
00:12:11,479 --> 00:12:12,440
Sedang bersih-bersih?

196
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:13,320
Direktur Lin.

197
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,719
Kau datang mencari Direktur Lei, 'kan?

198
00:12:16,479 --> 00:12:17,640
